==Useful Info==
'''Worker ants''' are tasty insects that behave much like [[adder]]s: they are fast, poisonous, and only a real threat to low-level characters. Expect them to hit somewhat harder though. They can be found in the early [[Dungeon]].

==Tips & Tricks==
*Wounding or killing them at range will minimize their ability to poison you in melee.
*They are vulnerable to poison. [[Poisonous Vapours]] and other [[Poison Magic]] work very well against them, as do [[venom]]-branded weapons and [[dart]]s.

==History==
*Worker ants were removed in [[0.27]].
